---
/* Small corner tag placed on featured cards (bottom-right). The card it sits in
   must be `relative`. */
---
<span class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-4 right-4 z-10 rounded-full border border-accent/30 bg-accent/10 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[0.62rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">
  Featured
</span>
